---
source: crates/tk/tests/scenarios.rs
expression: "p.run(&format!(\"{command} --help\"))"
---
Inspect or configure the current Workspace Scope

Usage: tk worktree [COMMAND]

Commands:
  set    Configure Workspace Scope for this worktree
  clear  Remove the configured Workspace Scope
  start  Create a Ticket branch and scoped git worktree

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
